OL,3,CThree in four universities 'could be
OL,4,Cin deficit by next year'
OL,6,FThe Chancellor says the UK's
OL,7,Funiversities are in a "very difficult
OL,8,Fsituation" after 14 years of
OL,9,FConservative government
OL,11,FThree out of four universities will
OL,12,Flikely be running a financial deficit
OL,13,Fby the next academic year, according
OL,14,Fto new government figures.
OL,16,FThe Office for Students (OfS) said up
OL,17,Fto 72% of higher education providers
OL,18,Fcould fall below the line by 2025-26
OL,19,Fbased on current trends, with a
OL,20,Freduction in student numbers a
OL,21,Fsignificant factor.
