OL,3,CThree in four universities 'could be
OL,4,Cin deficit by next year'
OL,6,FA large part of the reason is an
OL,7,Festimated drop of #3.4bn in income
OL,8,Facross the sector.
OL,10,FThe forecast of three quarters in
OL,11,Fdeficit by next year is a dramatic
OL,12,Fupgrade of OfS analysis in May which
OL,13,Fpredicted nearly two-thirds would be
OL,14,Fin deficit by 2026.
OL,16,FIt comes less than two weeks after the
OL,17,FEducation Secretary announced tuition
OL,18,Ffees in England would rise to #9,535
OL,19,Fnext year to "secure the future of
OL,20,Fhigher education."
