OL,6,FIn its new report published on Friday,
OL,7,Fthe OfS looked at the latest available
OL,8,Fdata trends for the recruitment of UK
OL,9,Fand international students for entry
OL,10,Fin autumn 2024.
OL,12,FIt estimated that UK undergraduate
OL,13,Fentrants and non-UK entrants were 10%
OL,14,Fand 23% lower than sector forecasts
OL,15,Ffor this academic year respectively.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
