OL,6,FWhile acceptances of UK undergraduate
OL,7,Fstudents through Ucas increased by
OL,8,F1.3% (4,445) in 2024 compared with the
OL,9,Fsame point last year, the figure is
OL,10,Fsignificantly below the forecast of a
OL,11,F5.8% increase.
OL,13,FAnalysis of the data suggests there
OL,14,Fwere 16% fewer visa applications made
OL,15,Fby international students in 2024 than
OL,16,Fin 2023.
