OL,6,FAround 100 providers failed to achieve
OL,7,Ftheir UK undergraduate recruitment
OL,8,Fforecasts for 2024-25, while 150
OL,9,Fproviders may have failed to achieve
OL,10,Fforecast levels of international
OL,11,Frecruitment, the report said.
OL,13,FCertain countries which previously
OL,14,Fsent significant numbers to study in
OL,15,Fthe UK, such as Nigeria and
OL,16,FBangladesh, saw their student
OL,17,Fenrolment here decrease by more than
OL,18,F40%.
