OL,6,FThe modelling includes changes to the
OL,7,Ftuition fee levels and the increase in
OL,8,Fnational insurance contributions for
OL,9,Femployers announced in the budget, but
OL,10,Fassumes no growth in UK postgraduate
OL,11,Fstudents.
OL,13,FA report by the Higher Education
OL,14,FPolicy Institute think tank published
OL,15,Flast month warned many universities
OL,16,Ffaced a "very bleak" future as student
OL,17,Fdemand for higher education could fall
OL,18,Fafter 2030 due to a shrinking 18-year-
OL,19,Fold population.
