OL,11,FOfS chief executive Susan Lapworth
OL,12,Fsaid: "Today's report demonstrates
OL,13,Fjust how challenging recruitment is
OL,14,Ffor many institutions, with modelling
OL,15,Fsuggesting that many more institutions
OL,16,Fwill report a deficit and low
OL,17,Fliquidity than had been forecast."
