OL,3,CThree in four universities 'could be
OL,4,Cin deficit by next year'
OL,6,FMs Lapworth said larger research-
OL,7,Fintensive and teaching-intensive
OL,8,Funiversities were in better financial
OL,9,Fshape than other types of
OL,10,Finstitutions, and that medium and
OL,11,Fsmaller-sized institutions, along with
OL,12,Fspecialist providers, were more likely
OL,13,Fto be affected by financial challenges
OL,14,Fgoing forward.
OL,16,FVivienne Stern MBE, chief executive of
OL,17,FUniversities UK, said the OfS's new
OL,18,Fanalysis was "a source of serious
OL,19,Fconcern. Universities in all four
OL,20,Fnations of the UK are in an extremely
OL,21,Fdifficult position."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
